WAFFLEBURGERS BACK

and look what i brought with me, 

a total revamp of your favorite hosties map, boardwalk! yes yes, i have realized some of the weaknesses of the map and have fixed them!

list of changes:

-rebel way (!)
-improved fps
-waffleburger's house o' fish restaurant
-better scenery
-revamped displacements
-and much much more!

so go ahead, download it, upload it, whatever! 


P.S. pm me if you put it on your server. you dont need to ask for my permission, but it would be appreciated if i knew :P
